    "(17)Note that unlike the following Theorems, this proof does not rely on any assumptions on D.We now consider a graph with edge weights drawn from an arbitrary distribution with mean value µ and standard deviation σ.",
    "To study the infinite-size limit, we define a quantity that tends to a constant as D → ∞.",
